page.title: 10RANSKILL SCOUTS & CUBS
page.content: Our local cubs are the 2nd.Ranskill Cubs who meet at the Church Hall every Thursday at 6.30pm-8.00pm, the leaders include my mum(Mrs.Margaret Parnell), Mrs.skelton and Mrs.Rynberk.I was once a cub, but i'm too old now(i'm 11),i'm a scout now at 1st. Sutton-Cum-Lound, (there are no Scouts at Ranskill at the moment because know one wants to run it.Though there is some interest now someone may run the Scouts.)The cubs go camping once or twice a year, they go camping at Sheffield(Greno Woods),where Scout leaders Dave & Barry keep them in order!This year for the first time the cubs are going on a circus fun camp at Walesby.With lots of cups,trophies and events to keep them out of mischief!(They're quite good really.)We win quite alot of cups,trophies and events.
